	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Actually I think a 100k pot is more useful for the audio mod; or at least, it's what I did, and it helps a lot. The balance of the various expansions isn't really that great in the current powerpak mappers so it's good to be able to adjust. I also use famicom carts in my NES with an adapter sometimes, and I've really appreciated having the pot.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


