<br />Thanks for the suggestion.  I would certainly be open to putting 100k pots on the board if I order another batch, but I already have the first 40 PCBs in hand.  The existing footprint can take up to a 1/4w through hole resistor so I just need to figure out which one.  If there's no real difference between those two for this purpose, I'd just as soon go with the 1/8w carbon film.

		

